Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.15,On Screen,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[Kagura]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.25,Main01,KAGURA,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastně Shinpachi, ty jsi taky celý bílý.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:42.88,On Screen,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[Shinpachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:42.76,Main01,SHINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,To vím.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:43.51,On Screen,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[Kagura, Gintoki]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:43.76,Main01,KAGURA  GINTOKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:48.62,On Screen,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[Gintoki]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.10,Main01,GINTOKI,0000,0000,0000,,Ty víš?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:48.83,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak řekni nám, Shinpachi.\NCo se sakra děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.83,Main01,KAGURA,0000,0000,0000,,Proč se to děje?
