Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:54.57,Main01,SHINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Je to všechno chyba toho chlapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.39,On Screen,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[Kagura, Gintoki]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:55.68,Main01,KAGURA  GINTOKI,0000,0000,0000,,Toho chlapa?
