Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.91,On Screen,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,300)}[V-mezi animaci]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:09.09,Main01,SHINPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,V mezi animaci je roztroušená všude.
