Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:55.80,Main01,CLOSING SONGPREVIEWHAGA,0000,0000,0000,,At 7:25 on February 21st, the defendant Taizo Hasegawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:57.73,Main01,CLOSING SONGPREVIEWHAGA,0000,0000,0000,,forcefully grabbed the hand of the victim, Ms. A,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:01.81,Main01,CLOSING SONGPREVIEWHAGA,0000,0000,0000,,on the platform at Kabukicho station and dragged her down into the railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:05.98,Main01,CLOSING SONGPREVIEWHAGA,0000,0000,0000,,He is suspected of performing a Kinniku Buster in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:08.05,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly an act of molestation and assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:12.90,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,And depending on the circumstance, it may even be considered attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.90,0:24:13.83,Main01,GINTOKI,0000,0000,0000,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.83,0:24:18.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the defendant performed a Kinniku Buster on the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.15,0:24:23.51,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,However it is questionable as to whether he did this with the intent to molest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:26.91,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore, I plead that the defendant is not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:29.95,On Screen,TITLE,0000,0000,0000,,["Men, Be A Madao"]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.95,0:24:36.62,On Screen red,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[Attorney Sakata vs. Prosecutor Haga. The battle has begun.]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:39.89,On Screen red,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,[And will Hasegawa be able to win against the Heidi living inside him?]
